<main>
  <!-- Box: Compartilhar -->
<div class="custom-box-sidebar p-3">
  <h4 class="fw-semibold"><i class="bi bi-share-fill me-2"></i>Compartilhe</h4>
  <form action="/memorial/{{slug}}/invite" method="POST" class="mt-2">
    <div class="mb-2">
      <label for="emailConvite" class="form-label visually-hidden">E-mail do convidado</label>
      <input type="email" id="emailConvite" name="email" class="form-control form-control-sm" placeholder="E-mail do convidado" required>
    </div>
    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary w-100">
      <i class="bi bi-envelope-plus me-1"></i> Enviar convite
    </button>
  </form>
  <ul class="list-unstyled small mt-3">
    <li>Convide amigos e familiares para visitar este memorial.</li>
    <li>Mantenha viva na memória as lembranças.</li>
  </ul>
</div>


  <!-- Box: Estatísticas -->
  <div class="custom-box-sidebar my-0 mx-0 p-3">
    <h4 class="fw-semibold"><i class="bi bi-bar-chart-fill me-2"></i>Estatísticas</h4>
    <p><strong>Visitas:</strong> {{estatisticas.totalVisitas}}</p>
    <p><strong>Tributos:</strong> {{estatisticas.totalTributos}}</p>
    <p><strong>Histórias de Vida:</strong> {{estatisticas.totalHistorias}}</p>
    <p><strong>Histórias Compartilhadas:</strong> {{estatisticas.totalHistoriasCom}}</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Box: Galeria com Link -->
  <a href="/memorial/{{slug}}/gallery" class="text-decoration-none text-dark">
    <div class="custom-box-sidebar my-0 mx-0 p-3 hover-shadow">
      <h4 class="fw-semibold"><i class="bi bi-images me-2"></i>Galeria</h4>
      {{#if gallery.photos.length}}
        <div class="row g-2">
          {{#each gallery.photos}}
            <div class="col-6">
              <img src="/memorials/{{../slug}}/photos/{{this.filename}}" class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm custom-sidebar-photo" alt="Foto de {{../firstName}}">
            </div>
          {{/each}}
        </div>
      {{else}}
        <p class="text-muted">Nenhuma foto disponível.</p>
      {{/if}}
    </div>
  </a>
</main>
